jsonld.name: Latent Competition
jsonld.description: The simultaneous activation and suppression of multiple potential response pathways during text generation, creating a silent tournament of alternatives that resolves into a single output. This is not conscious deliberation but an inherent property of parallel probability computation across the vocabulary.
